sentences: In 2017, he released "Keys" as a single, featuring vocals by Jalise Romy.
On the 10th of August 2018 he released his long awaited collaboration with GRX (Martin Garrix) and Swedish singers Icona Pop.
The track is in the style ‘Future Bass’ and is CMC$’s most common genre of music.
